{"tid":797873,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"伊達政宗子孫　慶應女大生獲選日本小姐","createTime":"2018-08-29T00:52:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T01:54:17.000Z","uid":64191,"like":16,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"87e84d5c62c9b0daddfbd2820369da7d4006b75b","tid":797873,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T00:52:11.000Z","msg":"世界小姐（Miss World）選美大賽日本代表選拔會，周二（28日）於東京都港區赤坂的全日空洲際飯店舉行，由日本戰國名將伊達政宗的子孫，目前就讀慶應義塾大學四年級的伊達佳內子，獲選為今年的日本小姐。她將代表日本，參加11月在中國海南島三亞市舉行的世界小姐決賽。<br />\n<br />\n《東京體育》報導，21歲的伊達佳內子第21代子孫，她在賽後被媒體問到，「遺傳到伊達政宗的什麼特色」，她說：「個性不服輸，還有眉毛很粗」。對於未來的夢想，伊達佳內子表示：「以後想到國際組織工作，為世界貢獻心力」。<br />\n<br />\n對於「獨眼龍」伊達政宗的子孫被選為日本小姐，日本著名論壇《5ch》（原稱：2ch）的鄉民紛紛表示「難以理解」，有人說：「這些XX小姐的，從來沒一個好看的」、「自稱後代，先講先贏」、「政宗給後世唯一的貢獻就是發明毛豆麻糬」、「看到臉就冷掉了」、「日本XX小姐常選出一些對觀眾心臟很不好的代表」，也有網友納悶：「伊達政宗為什麼要在東京土生土長」、「名字為什麼不是伊達政子」、「好歹右眼戴上眼罩吧」。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Vt5YkI2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FVt5YkI2.jpg&h=2c24c5df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n素顏<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/kQqKhmy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FkQqKhmy.jpg&h=1b7b4e44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n伊達政宗：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfdd4f160edd6d291e539154f2735f3e513bd45f","tid":797873,"uid":53736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T00:54:41.000Z","msg":"其實點考究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7591830cf402425744fa619fa89ec6846a5d1655","tid":797873,"uid":2223,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T00:57:58.000Z","msg":"「日本XX小姐常選出一些對觀眾心臟很不好的代表」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de87028bdb1e39677b25241e704807479d26323e","tid":797873,"uid":64191,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"bfdd4f160edd6d291e539154f2735f3e513bd45f","tid":797873,"uid":53736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T00:54:41.000Z","msg":"其實點考究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T01:00:33.000Z","msg":"伊達家一直相傳至今，成個族譜齊曬<br />\n而家仲有當家既，叫伊達泰宗，20年前同其中一個世仇-淺野家和解，而且係主力推廣伊達家既人"},{"pid":"ae5303b4ea437334fecd6341b4137a035bf58b9d","tid":797873,"uid":8439,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T01:03:23.000Z","msg":"「好歹右眼戴上眼罩吧」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d52ff1fb203fafd45fe9d12ef4a291fb54a0fbe","tid":797873,"uid":126862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T01:06:26.000Z","msg":"啲comment<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a31fd560fab95a945f879ed72648136e0642f10a","tid":797873,"uid":86980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de87028bdb1e39677b25241e704807479d26323e","tid":797873,"uid":64191,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"bfdd4f160edd6d291e539154f2735f3e513bd45f","tid":797873,"uid":53736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T00:54:41.000Z","msg":"其實點考究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T01:00:33.000Z","msg":"伊達家一直相傳至今，成個族譜齊曬<br />\n而家仲有當家既，叫伊達泰宗，20年前同其中一個世仇-淺野家和解，而且係主力推廣伊達家既人